app_description: Cherish offers these features! One sentence you want to remember Write down a message to yourself. Simply reading it every day will give you a lot of strength. Diary with music Keep a diary while listening to the calm background music. It will help you record your thoughts. Write about yourself using 3 different diary formats The diary presents a diary guide for strangers. Choose the format of the diary you want to write today and fill it out. Look at your emotions Keep a diary with any subject you want Take question recommendations
